summary: Blurb about harry telling you how much he supports you and loves you and he can’t stop smiling and kissing and cuddling you💖💖💖
question: Blurb about harry telling you how much he supports you and loves you and he can’t stop smiling and kissing and cuddling you💖💖💖
answer:
STOP IT :-(

-

He is a very cheeky guy.

There’s just a time in his life where he is just so in love, he can’t even get his hands away from you for just a second. He would always crave for everything about you, and you didn’t care, you love it.

“My bubba.” He cooed at you as he sat on the bed while he looked at you on the mirror, fixing your hair.

You laughed and shook your head, it was happening again, not that you’re complaining, but you weren’t surprised, you were actually expecting this.

Harry looked over your bookshelves, some of them are containing of the books you wrote, which took you a lot of time for you to finish it. He can’t really express on how much he was proud of you.

“So proud of you, bub. I know I don’t say it very often, but I truly am proud of you.” He smiled, your heart melted as you saw his smile were from ear to ear, you were so thankful for it. You went up and gave him a tight hug, slowly straddling his lap as he wrapped his arms around you.

“Thank you.” You smiled back at him, and gave his forehead a kiss. He grinned happily and laid down the bed, he had has his arms around you, keeping you secured on his chest. You barely became the little spoon, because most likely you were the big spoon.

“I love you.” Harry whispered as he planted kisses on your cheeks up to your forehead. His hold were becoming tighter and tighter but you couldn’t care less.

“Love you so much, bub.” He stared at your eyes a little, but before you could even say it back, he pressed his lips against yours, cupping your cheeks as he slowly went on top of you.

His kisses were soft and gentle, not like when he is needy or horny. He pulled away, and planted some kisses again on your chest and up to your neck, and slowly lying down on your chest. You giggled on how fast you became the big spoon now.

“I love you very much.” He said it slowly.

“I love you too, H.” You smiled down at him.
